title: 246: 10 Takeaways from Week 15
itunes:title: 246: 10 Takeaways from Week 15
description:
Daniel Jeremiah and Bucky Brooks recap the huge weekend that was in the NFL. Are the Vikings the best team in the NFC (17:55)? Will we see a Patriots and Steelers rematch in the AFC Championship (00:52)? Are Bortles (5:30) and Foles (8:18) good enough to lead their teams to the Super Bowl? All that and much more on this episode of Move the Sticks presented by the Ford F-Series.
